# Benchmarks

- Reports live in `runtime/state/benchmarks/*.json` and must conform to `runtime/schemas/benchmark_report.schema.json`.
- Include baselines, seeds, data splits, and known limitations.
- Never cherry-pick runs; link each row to `runtime/state/experiment_provenance.yaml`.
- Negative or null results belong in provenance `negative_results`, not omitted from reports.
